                <div class="post-content">
                        <p>Today I had the opportunity to give a conference to a group of students at the University of Alberta. Afterwards, I took some time to talk to a few of the students in attendance to get their impressions on the session and Hyperthinking. I found their takeaways inspiring. It&#8217;s always interesting to see which key points of Hyperthinking individuals take home and apply in their daily lives.</p>
